by James W. Morris, Ph.D., P.E., Jere Northrop, Ph.D., George W. Bloom, P.E., and Steve Pagano. From the proceedings of the 2005 Animal Waste Management Symposium, Research Triangle Park, NC, October 5-7, 2005
